Hello All.....

This is all about to enable machine learning on Windows 10

Its very simple and easy.

Step 1:
https://anaconda.org/anaconda/python
**Click on this link to to download anaconda for windows 10

Above The page there will be wriiten "Download Anaconda"
Click on that 
Then Click on Windows icon/logo

scroll below 
download .installer according to system that is 64 bit or 32 bit

after downloading is finished
click on the installer and install anaconda.

to check whether anaconda is installed or not type anaconda navigator in windows search bar and click on it

Your default anaconda package will be base(root)

you can run simple programs using jupyter notebook.

